{"tid":41604,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"無咗中意人嗰種感覺","createTime":"2016-12-16T04:22:27.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-16T04:26:49.000Z","uid":49971,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"112435121c215551ada307abf5518426c6d4958f","tid":41604,"uid":49971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T04:22:27.000Z","msg":"ex俾咗帽我戴 已經散咗就一年<br />\n一年裡面遇過唔同嘅女仔 <br />\n但始終搵唔翻中意人嗰種感覺<br />\n<br />\n到而家我都仲開住佢ig既帖子通知<br />\n可能只係習慣咗開住<br />\n<br />\n呢一年裡面我同佢都無再拍過拖（據我所知）<br />\n我一路都覺得我對佢已經無感覺 已經放低咗<br />\n但有時夜晚一個 我就會諗<br />\n如果佢有一日post咗張佢同仔嘅合照 佢同人拍拖<br />\n我會唔會真係無感覺？<br />\n<br />\n我唔知我一直都無想再識女仔既原因<br />\n係因為未放低ex 定純粹因為未遇到啱嘅女仔<br />\n<br />\nsor for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f146e8aa052560749157f3966766fce72dbfb79","tid":41604,"uid":38293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T04:22:50.000Z","msg":"55"},{"pid":"a8252e5bc3f95db5506e6a6c67854f29a19fe03b","tid":41604,"uid":22715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T04:23:49.000Z","msg":"嗯"},{"pid":"5c4ddaab245471052611011602eccf4a057e7a42","tid":41604,"uid":38428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T04:24:14.000Z","msg":"咁仲有無同佢講嘢"},{"pid":"d783a6b1fca41f0c394a79d5b6c76a915291c5ba","tid":41604,"uid":49971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T04:26:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁仲有無同佢講嘢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢間唔中whatsapp我<br />\n我會特登覆得冷淡 一句起兩句止"}]}